---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 space-y-5 text-gray-300">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-left underline">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="mb-6">
      At <strong>Hypixel Stats</strong>, we value your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your data.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Data Collection</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect any personal data from visitors. All server statistics are retrieved publicly via Hypixel's official API.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Use of Data</h2>
        <p>
          The data displayed on this site is for informational purposes only and reflects live server statistics such as online player count and server status.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may use third-party APIs like Hypixelâ€™s API or Mojang API to fetch public data. These services are governed by their own privacy policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us via our official support channel.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
      This project is licensed under the <a class="text-blue-500 underline" href="https://opensource.org/license/mit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MIT License</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
